NKICBCL_114.Description: Sum of scores of items 14-Cries a lot, 29-Fears, 30-Fears school, 31-Fears doing bad, 32-Must be perfect, 33-Feels unloved, 35-Feels worthless, 45-Nervous, tense 50-Fearful, anxious 52-Feels too guilty, 71-Self-conscious, 91-Talks or thinks of suicide, 112-Worries. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_14] + [NKICBCL_29A] + [NKICBCL_30] + [NKICBCL_31] + [NKICBCL_32] + [NKICBCL_33] + [NKICBCL_35] + [NKICBCL_45] + [NKICBCL_50] + [NKICBCL_52] + [NKICBCL_71] + [NKICBCL_91] + [NKICBCL_112]

NKICBCL_115.Description: Sum of scores of items 5-Enjoys little, 42-Rather be alone, 65-Won’t talk, 69-Secretive, 75-Shy, timid, 102-Lacks energy, 103-Sad, 111-Withdrawn. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_05] + [NKICBCL_42] + [NKICBCL_65] + [NKICBCL_69] + [NKICBCL_75] + [NKICBCL_102] + [NKICBCL_103] + [NKICBCL_111]

NKICBCL_116.Description: Sum of scores of items 47-Nightmares, 49-Constipated, 51-Feels dizzy, 54-Overtired, 56a-Aches, pain, 56b-Headaches, 56c-Nausea, 56da-Eye problems, 56e-Skin problems, 56f-Stomachaches, 56g-Vomiting. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_47] + [NKICBCL_49] + [NKICBCL_51] + [NKICBCL_54] + [NKICBCL_56A] + [NKICBCL_56B] + [NKICBCL_56C] + [NKICBCL_56DA] + [NKICBCL_56E] + [NKICBCL_56F] + [NKICBCL_56G]

NKICBCL_117.Description: Sum of scores of items 11-Too dependent, 12-Lonely, 25-Doesn’t get along, 27-Jealous, 34-Others out to get him/her, 36-Accident-prone, 38-Gets teased, 48-Not liked, 62-Clumsy, 64-Prefers younger kids, 79-Speech problems. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_11] + [NKICBCL_12] + [NKICBCL_25] + [NKICBCL_27] + [NKICBCL_34] + [NKICBCL_36] + [NKICBCL_38] + [NKICBCL_48] + [NKICBCL_62] + [NKICBCL_64] + [NKICBCL_79A]

NKICBCL_118.Description: Sum of scores of items 9a-Can’t get mind off thoughts, 18-Harms self, 40a-Hears things, 46a-Twitching, 58a-Picks skin, 59-Sex parts in public, 60-Sex parts too much, 66a-Repeats acts, 70a-Sees things, 76-Sleeps less, 83a-Stores things, 84a-Strange behavior, 85a-Strange ideas, 92a-Sleep talks/walks, 100a-Trouble sleeping. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_9A] + [NKICBCL_18] + [NKICBCL_40A] + [NKICBCL_46A] + [NKICBCL_58A] + [NKICBCL_59] + [NKICBCL_60] + [NKICBCL_66A] + [NKICBCL_70A] + [NKICBCL_76] + [NKICBCL_83A] + [NKICBCL_84A] + [NKICBCL_85A] + [NKICBCL_92A] + [NKICBCL_100A]

NKICBCL_119.Description: Sum of scores of items 01-Acts young, 4-Fails to finish, 8-Can’t concentrate, 10-Can’t sit still, 13-Confused, 17-Daydreams, 41-Impulsive, 61-Poor schoolwork, 78-Inattentive, 80-Stares blankly. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_01] + [NKICBCL_04] + [NKICBCL_08] + [NKICBCL_10] + [NKICBCL_13] + [NKICBCL_17] + [NKICBCL_41] + [NKICBCL_61] + [NKICBCL_78] + [NKICBCL_80]

NKICBCL_120.Description: Sum of scores of items 2a-Drinks alcohol, 26-Lacks guilt, 28-Breaks rules, 39-Bad friends, 43-Lies, cheats, 63-Prefers older kids, 67-Runs away, 72-Sets fires, 73a-Sex problems, 81-Steals at home, 82-Steals outside home, 90-Swearing, 96-Thinks of sex too much, 99-Uses tobacco, 101-Truant, 105a-Uses drugs, 106-Vandalism. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_02A] + [NKICBCL_26] + [NKICBCL_28] + [NKICBCL_39] + [NKICBCL_43] + [NKICBCL_63] + [NKICBCL_67] + [NKICBCL_72] + [NKICBCL_73A] + [NKICBCL_81] + [NKICBCL_82] + [NKICBCL_90] + [NKICBCL_96] + [NKICBCL_99] + [NKICBCL_101] + [NKICBCL_105A] + [NKICBCL_106]

NKICBCL_121.Description: Sum of scores of items 3-Argues a lot, 16-Mean to others, 19-Demands attention, 20-Destroys own things, 21-Destroys others’ things, 22-Disobedient at home, 23-Disobedient at school, 37-Gets in fights, 57-Attacks people, 68-Screams a lot, 86-Stubborn, sullen, 87-Mood changes, 88-Sulks, 89-Suspicious, 94-Teases a lot, 95-Temper, 97-Threatens others, 104-Loud. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_03] + [NKICBCL_16] + [NKICBCL_19] + [NKICBCL_20] + [NKICBCL_21] + [NKICBCL_22] + [NKICBCL_23] + [NKICBCL_37] + [NKICBCL_57] + [NKICBCL_68] + [NKICBCL_86] + [NKICBCL_87] + [NKICBCL_88] + [NKICBCL_89] + [NKICBCL_94] + [NKICBCL_95] + [NKICBCL_97] + [NKICBCL_104]

NKICBCL_122.Description: Sum of scores of items 6-BM outside toilet, 7-Bragging, boasting, 15-Cruel to animals, 24-Doesn’t eat well, 44-Bites finger nails, 53-Overeating, 55-Overweight, 56ha-Other physical, 74-Showing off, clowning, 77a-Sleeps more, 93-Talks too much, 98-Thumb-sucking, 107-Wets self (day), 108-Wets the bed, 109-Whining, 110-Wishes to be opposite sex, 113a-Other problems. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_06] + [NKICBCL_07] + [NKICBCL_15] + [NKICBCL_24] + [NKICBCL_44] + [NKICBCL_53] + [NKICBCL_55] + [NKICBCL_56HA] + [NKICBCL_74] + [NKICBCL_77A] + [NKICBCL_93] + [NKICBCL_98] + [NKICBCL_107] + [NKICBCL_108] + [NKICBCL_109] + [NKICBCL_110] + [NKICBCL_113A]

NKICBCL_123.Description: Sum of Anxious/Depressed, Withdrawn/depressed, and Somatic Complaints Subscores. This grouping is called “Internalizing,” because it comprises problems that are mainly within the self. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_114] + [NKICBCL_115] + [NKICBCL_116]

NKICBCL_124.Description: Sum of Rule-Breaking Behavior and Aggressive Behavior Subscores. This grouping is called “Externalizing,” because it comprises problems that mainly involve conflicts with other people and with their expectations for the child. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_120] + [NKICBCL_121]

NKICBCL_125.Description: Sum of Social Problems, Thought Problems, Attention Problems, and Other Problems subscores. | Calculation = [NKICBCL_117] + [NKICBCL_118] + [NKICBCL_119] + [NKICBCL_122]

NKICBCL_126.Description: Sum of Social Problems, Thought Problems, Attention Problems, Other Problems, Internalizing Behaviors and Externalizing Behaviors. A child’s Total Problems score can range from 0 (if the respondent scored every problem 0) to 240 (if the respondent scored every problem 2). | Calculation = [NKICBCL_123] + [NKICBCL_124] + [NKICBCL_125]
